br />\n討論：<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2116545\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2116545</a><br />\nTG： <a href=\"http://t.me/AntiFCWalkover\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2FAntiFCWalkover&d=bKbBxrmwQkzC5eAvTqWhP7eFZk%2BLn%2Bp4m9s6a9hK%2BPA%3D&h=f3424e2e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">t.me/AntiFCWalkover</a><br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"gold\"><span class=\"xx-large\">呢12個界别要人吖<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />勸合資格嘅朋友、家人、同事參選吖<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span>"},{"pid":"73770ef7810334ed818f78ef75fc4450164c8213","tid":2117633,"uid":39277,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-21T05:28:06.000Z","msg":"其實喺出面搞ngo <br />\n搵啲有名氣嘅香港人聯絡各國人權組織，遊說啲國際名人加入依個ngo <br />\n再搵啲受害人上啲聽證會到講番啲經歷<br />\n<br />\n你三不五時你啲國際媒體陳述番受害經歷，得到更多關注，仲可以向對方施加壓力<br />\n<br />\n依加721、831、新屋嶺都無乜人再講"},{"pid":"f49f3ec16744ba9a50637fc93257559021bcd9f1","tid":2117633,"uid":223428,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-21T05:29:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}